elements.name: Add a new processo with success

steps.name: the user clicks in the Processos menu option
the user clicks in the Novo Processo button
the user fills the value "1" to the "processo_vara" field in the Processo page
the user fills the value "123" to the "processo_numero_processo" field in the Processo page
the user fills the value "Guarda" to the "processo_natureza" field in the Processo page
the user fills the value "Parte A x Parte B" to the "processo_partes" field in the Processo page
the user fills the value "14/03/2020" to the "processo_data_entrada" field in the Processo page
the user fills the value "Agendado" to the "processo_status" field in the Processo page
the user selects the option "Sim" int the Arbitramento field
the user selects the option "Não" int the "processo_urgente" field
the user clicks in the "btn-save" in the Processo page
the user should see the "Processo foi criado com sucesso." message in the Mostrar Processo page
the user is in the Agapito Software testing page
